	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Prestantissime <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bulingere</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quantum ad pericula, ad martiria nescio, si dominus eam mihi coronam reservet.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Redeundum est in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italiam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Inprimis tam ipse quam alii rogabitis sedulo patrem cęlestem, ut det mihi spiritum confidentię et gloriam suam in nobis et per nos in dies promoveat.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Deinde curabis quamprimum ad me mitti, quaqs historias depingi malueris in illis vasis.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego, quantum tibi et reliquis Helvetiorum ministris debeam ob receptam ab omnibus humanitatem, exprimere re ipsa mallem quam verbis agnoscere.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Me igitur habebitis semper addictissimum, ita faxit deus aliqua sese mihi occasio eofferet vobis alique in re gratificandi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribam ad te sedulo, si quid fuerit novum; ita tu vicissim ad me rescribas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerus</persName> nomine meo petiit a <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvino</persName> aliquot exemplaria astronomiam, de Interim et quedam alia, et fortasse, sicuti mihi dixit, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1227" cert="high">Foscovero</persName> vestro bibliopolę reddentur, et cum primum redierit <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8101" cert="high">Lelius</persName>, curabis, ut per ipsum ad me transmittantur nunciando, quantum pecuniam sim pro illis missurus.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale in domino meque ames.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas tuas ad me vel <placeName ref="l96" cert="high">Clavennam</placeName> ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1976" cert="high">Augustinum</placeName> vel ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l36" cert="high">Bergomum</placeName> ad <persName type="auto_name">Franciscum Belinchettum</persName>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod si D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8101" cert="high">lelius</persName> nimis <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileę</placeName> immorabitur, optarem, ut per te ad <placeName ref="l96" cert="high">Clavennam</placeName> vel <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l36" cert="high">Bergomum</placeName> usque ad <persName type="citizen_name">Belinchettum</persName> transmittendos curarentur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="signature">[Unterschrift, Datum und Adresse fehlen; der untere Teil des Blattes ist abgeschnitten.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
